import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';

const NavigationBar = () => {
    return (
        <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark" expand="lg" sticky="top">
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Brand href="/">C++ Learning Platform</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="me-auto">
                        <Nav.Link href="/">Home</Nav.Link>
                        <NavDropdown title="Tutorials" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/intro">Introduction</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/syntax">Syntax</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/comments">Comments</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/variables">Variables</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/data-types">Data Types</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/user-input">User Input</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/conditions">Conditions</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/switch-case">Switch Case</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/loops">Loops</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/break-continue">Break/Continue</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/arrays">Arrays</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/structures">Structures</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/references">References</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/pointers">Pointers</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/functions">Functions</NavDropdown.Item>
                            <NavDropdown.Item href="/tutorials/oop">OOP</NavDropdown.Item>
                        </NavDropdown>
                        <Nav.Link href="/quizzes">Quizzes</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="/code-editor">Code Editor</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="/ai-assistant">AI Assistant</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
    );
};

export default NavigationBar;
